nodes.text: "New G-1 Starfighter!" was a Star Wars Roleplaying Game article written by Cory Herndon and published by Wizards of the Coast in 2001 on the Wizards of the Coast website. It detailed the G-1 starfighter, a starfighter built as a joint venture between the Gungan BullbaBong firm and the Theed Palace Space Vessel Engineering Corps.
